<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:urn="urn:EasyCruit">
   <soapenv:Header>
      <urn:AuthHeader>
         <Customer>{{customer}}</Customer>
         <Username>{{username}}</Username>
         <Password passwordEncoding="plain">
            <passwordString>{{password}}</passwordString>
         </Password>
      </urn:AuthHeader>
   </soapenv:Header>
   <soapenv:Body>
      <urn:CandidateImport>
         <urn:Candidate>
            <![CDATA[
                <Candidate language="gb">
                    <PersonalDetails>
                        <FirstName>{{$randomFirstName}}</FirstName>
                        <LastName>{{$randomLastName}}</LastName>
                        <MiddleName>{{$randomFirstName}}</MiddleName>
                        <RegistrationDate>{{formattedDateRecent}}</RegistrationDate>
                        <DateOfBirth>{{formattedDatePast}}</DateOfBirth>
                        <Email>{{$randomExampleEmail}}</Email>
                        <Gender>{{randomGender}}</Gender>
                        <Homepage>{{$randomUrl}}</Homepage>
                        <Initials>{{$randomNamePrefix}}</Initials>
                        <Nickname>{{$randomFirstName}}</Nickname>
                        <LastNameAffix>van</LastNameAffix>
                        <FamilyNameAffix>der</FamilyNameAffix>
                        <FamilyName>{{$randomLastName}}</FamilyName>
                        <PostalAddress>
                            <Country iso="no"/>
                            <County id="11"/>
                            <Municipality id="266"/>
                            <PostalArea>{{$randomStreetName}}</PostalArea>
                            <PostalCode>112233</PostalCode>
                            <Address>{{$randomStreetAddress}}</Address>
                        </PostalAddress>
                        <Phone type="private">+37100000001</Phone>
                        <Phone type="work">+37100000002</Phone>
                        <Phone type="cellular">+37100000003</Phone>
                        <CurrentEmploymentStatus id="4" />
                        <Title id="1"/>
                        <Nationality iso="nl"/>
                        <Reserved>false</Reserved>
                    </PersonalDetails>
                    <RetentionSettings>
                         <PeriodValue>6</PeriodValue>
                         <PeriodType>months</PeriodType>
                    </RetentionSettings>
                    <EmploymentHistory>
                        <Employment>
                            <StartDate>{{formattedDatePast}}</StartDate>
                            <EndDate>{{formattedDatePast}}</EndDate>
                            <JobCategory id="1"/>
                            <SubCategory id="1"/>
                            <WorkRole id="11"/>
                            <Sector id="4"/>
                            <EmployerName>{{$randomCompanyName}}</EmployerName>
                            <PositionTitle>{{$randomJobTitle}}</PositionTitle>
                            <PositionDescription>{{$randomJobDescriptor}}</PositionDescription>
                            <current id="false"/>
                        </Employment>
                        <Employment>
                            <StartDate>{{formattedDatePast}}</StartDate>
                            <EndDate>{{formattedDateRecent}}</EndDate>
                            <JobCategory id="1"/>
                            <SubCategory id="1"/>
                            <WorkRole id="11"/>
                            <Sector id="4"/>
                            <EmployerName>{{$randomCompanyName}}</EmployerName>
                            <PositionTitle>{{$randomJobTitle}}</PositionTitle>
                            <PositionDescription>{{$randomJobDescriptor}}</PositionDescription>
                            <current id="true"/>
                        </Employment>
                    </EmploymentHistory>
                    <EducationHistory>
                        <Education>
                            <StartDate>{{formattedDatePast}}</StartDate>
                            <EndDate>{{formattedDateRecent}}</EndDate>
                            <InstituteType id="2"/>
                            <AreaOfEducation id="1"/>
                            <Degree id="10"/>
                            <Country id="150"/>
                            <InstituteName>{{$randomCompanyName}}</InstituteName>
                            <Comments>{{$randomBsNoun}}</Comments>
                            <AverageGrade>{{$randomBs}}</AverageGrade>
                            <ResultPoints>1024</ResultPoints>
                            <ExaminationResults>Exceptional</ExaminationResults>
                            <current id="true"/>
                        </Education>
                        <Education>
                            <StartDate>{{formattedDatePast}}</StartDate>
                            <EndDate>{{formattedDatePast}}</EndDate>
                            <InstituteType id="4"/>
                            <AreaOfEducation id="11"/>
                            <Degree id="14"/>
                            <Country id="150"/>
                            <InstituteName>{{$randomCompanyName}}</InstituteName>
                            <Comments>{{$randomBsNoun}}</Comments>
                            <AverageGrade>{{$randomBs}}</AverageGrade>
                            <ResultPoints>1024</ResultPoints>
                            <ExaminationResults>Exceptional</ExaminationResults>
                            <current id="false"/>
                        </Education>
                    </EducationHistory>
                    <Certifications>
                        <Certification>
                            <StartDate>{{formattedDatePast}}</StartDate>
                            <EndDate>{{formattedDatePast}}</EndDate>
                            <Name>{{$randomCompanyName}}</Name>
                            <Description>{{$randomBs}}</Description>
                            <Duration>8 hours</Duration>
                        </Certification>
                        <Certification>
                            <StartDate>{{formattedDatePast}}</StartDate>
                            <EndDate>{{formattedDateRecent}}</EndDate>
                            <Name>{{$randomCompanyName}}</Name>
                            <Description>{{$randomBs}}</Description>
                            <Duration>Several weeks</Duration>
                        </Certification>
                    </Certifications>
                    <References>
                        <Reference>
                            <CompanyName>{{$randomCompanyName}}</CompanyName>
                            <PersonName>{{$randomFullName}}</PersonName>
                            <ContactInfo>{{$randomPhoneNumber}}, {{$randomStreetAddress}}</ContactInfo>
                        </Reference>
                        <Reference>
                            <CompanyName>{{$randomCompanyName}}</CompanyName>
                            <PersonName>{{$randomFullName}}</PersonName>
                            <ContactInfo>{{$randomPhoneNumber}}, {{$randomStreetAddress}}</ContactInfo>
                        </Reference>
                    </References>
                    <Offices>
                        <Office>
                            <StartDate>{{formattedDatePast}}</StartDate>
                            <EndDate>{{formattedDatePast}}</EndDate>
                            <Company>{{$randomCompanyName}}</Company>
                            <Name>{{$randomJobTitle}}</Name>
                            <current id="false"/>
                        </Office>
                        <Office>
                            <StartDate>{{formattedDatePast}}</StartDate>
                            <EndDate>{{formattedDateRecent}}</EndDate>
                            <Company>{{$randomCompanyName}}</Company>
                            <Name>{{$randomJobTitle}}</Name>
                            <current id="true"/>
                        </Office>
                    </Offices>
                    <Competencies name="Softskills">
                        <Competency id="1"/>
                        <Competency id="12"/>
                        <Competency id="25"/>
                    </Competencies>
                    <Competencies name="IT Knowledge">
                        <Competency>
                            <Name>Java</Name>
                            <Level id="2">Novice</Level>
                        </Competency>
                        <Competency>
                            <Name>Javascript</Name>
                            <Level id="4">Experienced</Level>
                        </Competency>
                    </Competencies>
                    <Competencies name="Language">
                        <Competency>
                            <Name>224</Name>
                            <Level id="2" type="speaking"/>
                            <Level id="3" type="reading"/>
                            <Level id="7" type="writing"/>
                        </Competency>
                        <Competency>
                            <Name>150</Name>
                            <Level id="8" type="speaking"/>
                            <Level id="8" type="reading"/>
                            <Level id="8" type="writing"/>
                        </Competency>
                    </Competencies>
                    <Competencies name="Driverlicense">
                        <Competency>
                            <Name>11</Name>
                            <Level>{{formattedDateRecent}}</Level>
                        </Competency>
                    </Competencies>
                    <Login>
                        <UserName>{{$randomUserName}}</UserName>
                        <Password>{{$randomPassword}}</Password>
                    </Login>
                    <Questions>
                        <Question id="{{miscQuestionRadioButtonId}}">
                            <Value id="{{miscQuestionRadioButtonAnswerId}}"/>
                        </Question>
                        <Question id="{{miscQuestionCheckboxId}}">
                            <Value id="{{miscQuestionCheckboxFirstSelection}}"/>
                            <Value id="{{miscQuestionCheckboxSecondSelection}}"/>
                        </Question>
                        <Question id="{{miscQuestionTextId}}">
                            <Value>This is the answer to this question {{$randomAbbreviation}}</Value>
                        </Question>
                    </Questions>
                    <Questions type="internal">
                        <Question id="{{miscQuestionHrClassificationId}}">
                            <Value>This is the answer to HR classification question for candidate profile {{$randomAbbreviation}}</Value>
                        </Question>
                    </Questions>
                </Candidate>
            ]]>
         </urn:Candidate>
      </urn:CandidateImport>
   </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>

<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:urn="urn:EasyCruit">
   <soapenv:Header>
      <urn:AuthHeader>
         <Customer>{{customer}}</Customer>
         <Username>{{username}}</Username>
         <Password passwordEncoding="plain">
            <passwordString>{{password}}</passwordString>
         </Password>
      </urn:AuthHeader>
   </soapenv:Header>
   <soapenv:Body>
      <urn:AddCandidateToRecruitingProject>
         <urn:CandidateId>{{lastCandidateId}}</urn:CandidateId>
         <urn:RecruitingProjectId>{{vacancyId}}</urn:RecruitingProjectId>
         <urn:DepartmentId>{{departmentId}}</urn:DepartmentId>
         <urn:RecruiterId>{{recruiterId}}</urn:RecruiterId>
         <urn:ProjectData>
            <urn:ApplicationLanguage>gb</urn:ApplicationLanguage>
            <urn:ApplicationDate>{{formattedDateRecent}}</urn:ApplicationDate>
            <urn:ApplicationStatus>withdrawn</urn:ApplicationStatus>
            <urn:ApplicationScore>10</urn:ApplicationScore>
            <urn:ApplicationChannel>api_call</urn:ApplicationChannel>
            <urn:CoverLetter>This is a test cover letter in text format for the application: {{$randomAbbreviation}}</urn:CoverLetter>
            <urn:Question id="{{applicationMiscQuestionTextId}}">This is an answer to the text question for the application</urn:Question>
            <urn:Question id="{{applicationMiscQuestionRadioButtonId}}">{{applicationMiscQuestionRadioButtonAnswerId}}</urn:Question>
         </urn:ProjectData>
      </urn:AddCandidateToRecruitingProject>
   </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>
